WEBVTT

00:02.735 --> 00:04.936
Sean Walker
was just an ordinary man...

00:05.004 --> 00:06.304
Sir, please sit--aah!

00:06.372 --> 00:07.305
Thrown into the middle

00:07.373 --> 00:09.774
of an extraordinary
conspiracy

00:09.841 --> 00:11.275
while on the run
from the law.

00:11.343 --> 00:12.810
I'm walking out
with Leila.

00:12.877 --> 00:16.175
He just rescued
his kidnapped fiancee,

00:16.244 --> 00:18.031
along with
one of her captors.

00:18.099 --> 00:19.564
He and I are gonna
have a little talk.

00:19.632 --> 00:20.882
And Sophia,

00:20.950 --> 00:23.016
the leader of a mysterious
group of prisoners...

00:23.084 --> 00:24.804
I didn't condone
any of this.

00:24.872 --> 00:27.017
Was keeping the peace
between the White House

00:27.085 --> 00:28.093
and her own people.

00:28.161 --> 00:29.400
Tell me what you know.

00:29.468 --> 00:30.406
Until one of them...

00:30.473 --> 00:32.087
His name is Thomas.

00:32.154 --> 00:35.177
Broke her free
from 60-year detainment.

00:35.245 --> 00:36.890
She will lead us
straight to Thomas.

00:36.958 --> 00:38.928
He's your new priority.

00:38.995 --> 00:41.342
Now a new pursuit begins.

00:41.410 --> 00:42.987
Rein him in,
like you said you could.

00:43.054 --> 00:45.032
And <i>The Event</i>
continues.

