01:16.689 --> 01:18.159
Hello?

01:18.212 --> 01:19.951
Sophia...

01:20.019 --> 01:22.627
It's me.

01:22.695 --> 01:25.100
What the hell
were you thinking?

01:25.168 --> 01:27.406
That's really the first thing
you want to say to me

01:27.476 --> 01:29.345
after 66 years?

01:29.413 --> 01:31.887
You almost killed
200 people.

01:31.955 --> 01:34.193
Nobody died,
and you're free.

01:34.261 --> 01:36.968
- Everything else is details.
- Not to me.

01:37.036 --> 01:39.040
And I am far from free.

01:39.108 --> 01:41.112
We have to assume
that Martinez is doing

01:41.180 --> 01:43.017
everything in his power
to track me.

01:43.085 --> 01:44.856
If only so I'll
lead them to you.

01:44.924 --> 01:47.830
You've drawn a lot
of attention to yourself.

01:47.898 --> 01:49.367
Simon's gonna give us
the details

01:49.434 --> 01:50.738
to their follow operation.

01:50.805 --> 01:53.377
We need to get you out
so we can get started.

01:53.444 --> 01:55.348
There's a change of clothes
in your bag.

01:55.416 --> 01:58.389
It's a safe bet that
yours are compromised.

01:58.456 --> 02:00.093
And then what?

02:00.161 --> 02:01.262
Then I want you to
wait for me

02:01.330 --> 02:03.100
to tell you what to do.

02:05.306 --> 02:07.409
Okay, she just passed
the Van Ness Station.

02:07.477 --> 02:10.483
The next station's two miles.
Metro Center.

02:10.551 --> 02:11.720
Very good, Mr. Murphy.

02:11.788 --> 02:12.822
Please confirm with Andrews

02:12.890 --> 02:14.158
that the predators
have scrambled.

02:14.226 --> 02:17.465
Agent Lee, once the drones
start transmitting video,

02:17.534 --> 02:18.835
I want it fed to your teams
on the ground.

02:18.903 --> 02:20.673
I'll set up
a dedicated overlay, sir.

02:20.740 --> 02:21.808
Where are we?

02:21.876 --> 02:24.581
Sophia's train
is proceeding east

02:24.648 --> 02:25.850
on the red line right now.

02:25.917 --> 02:27.452
It's approaching
the Metro Center Station.

02:27.521 --> 02:29.691
Are we sure she's still
on the train?

02:29.759 --> 02:31.294
We're getting a clear signal
from the scandium-46

02:31.362 --> 02:32.730
in her bloodstream.

02:32.798 --> 02:34.300
And how long will
the isotopes stay active?

02:34.367 --> 02:35.636
Seven hours.

02:35.704 --> 02:38.341
If she hasn't led us
to this man Thomas by then,

02:38.409 --> 02:39.978
we'll reacquire her.

02:40.046 --> 02:43.051
Thomas is the target
of the operation, not Sophia.

02:43.118 --> 02:44.353
I don't want her hurt.

02:44.421 --> 02:47.826
Sophia has proven herself
far from trustworthy.

02:47.894 --> 02:51.199
In my opinion, we must
consider her a threat.

02:51.267 --> 02:54.940
She survives this, Blake.
Am I clear?

02:56.978 --> 02:59.749
Pull me out if there are
any major developments.

02:59.816 --> 03:01.217
Yes, Mr. President.

03:01.285 --> 03:04.189
Sir, I'd like to
join my men in the field.

03:04.257 --> 03:05.859
Supervise their deployment
in person.

03:09.734 --> 03:11.336
Thomas, it's Simon.

03:11.403 --> 03:12.538
And we have a problem.

03:12.606 --> 03:14.108
They've got a tracker
in Sophia.

03:14.175 --> 03:15.243
In her?

03:15.311 --> 03:16.679
They put it in her food.

03:16.747 --> 03:18.048
It's a radioactive
isotope.

03:18.115 --> 03:19.183
While it's active,
they'll be able

03:19.251 --> 03:20.418
to track her
wherever she goes.

03:20.486 --> 03:22.255
There must be some way
to get it out.

03:22.323 --> 03:23.457
There isn't.

03:23.525 --> 03:25.594
But there may be another way
to deal with it.

03:25.662 --> 03:26.696
Good.

03:26.764 --> 03:29.500
I'm counting on you.

03:39.151 --> 03:40.886
Hey.

03:40.954 --> 03:41.921
How was it?

03:41.989 --> 03:43.090
Oh, it was nice.

03:43.157 --> 03:44.859
It looks rough.
You should come in.

03:44.927 --> 03:46.462
Hey, give me a kiss.

03:46.529 --> 03:49.667
No, it's--it's warm.

03:49.735 --> 03:51.303
I swear.

03:51.371 --> 03:52.471
You'll love it.

03:52.539 --> 03:54.609
I like watching you.
Yeah?

03:54.676 --> 03:57.579
Mm-hmm.
You look happy.

03:57.648 --> 04:01.653
Like you're discovering water
for the first time.

04:01.721 --> 04:05.191
Yeah, well, where I'm from
there wasn't any.

04:05.259 --> 04:08.530
You never talk
about your past.

04:08.598 --> 04:11.565
Well...

04:11.633 --> 04:14.534
When I'm with you...

04:14.601 --> 04:15.935
It doesn't matter.

04:16.002 --> 04:19.204
For the first time
in my life,

04:19.272 --> 04:21.272
I'm free of it.

04:26.411 --> 04:28.813
I love you, Mason.

04:33.852 --> 04:35.519
I love you.

04:35.587 --> 04:38.322
I love you too.

04:52.734 --> 04:55.302
Hey, have Sophia get off

04:55.370 --> 04:57.403
at the Gallery Place Station
and walk east.

04:57.471 --> 05:01.507
By that time, I'll know
if this will work.

05:01.574 --> 05:03.042
Change of plans.

05:03.109 --> 05:05.010
They've deployed a radioactive
isotope in your bloodstream.

05:05.078 --> 05:06.879
How?

05:06.946 --> 05:08.914
Your friend Martinez
put it in your food.

05:23.893 --> 05:25.427
Sir, she just got off
at a stop.

05:25.495 --> 05:27.028
Location?

05:27.096 --> 05:28.496
Uh, Ggallery.

05:28.564 --> 05:30.965
It's Chinatown.

05:35.470 --> 05:39.573
Get up to the street
and take an immediate left.

05:39.640 --> 05:41.674
Command just reported
the target exited

05:41.741 --> 05:44.009
the Gallery Place Station.
What's your position?

05:44.077 --> 05:45.744
We're three blocks away from
the station and closing.

05:45.812 --> 05:46.979
No, hold your approach.

05:47.046 --> 05:50.048
I don't want the team
getting any closer.

05:50.115 --> 05:51.615
Ahead of you
is Sixth Street.

05:51.683 --> 05:54.118
Gonna make a left,
continue on.

05:54.185 --> 05:56.953
Across the street you will see
the place I've been describing.

05:57.021 --> 05:59.022
Oh.

06:02.025 --> 06:03.658
Okay, she's on to Sixth,

06:03.726 --> 06:05.393
crossing east,
entering a building.

06:05.461 --> 06:08.629
Which is...

06:08.697 --> 06:12.299
It's a coffee shop.

06:12.366 --> 06:14.901
Is it possible she's
stopping for coffee?

06:14.968 --> 06:17.103
Thank you.

06:45.127 --> 06:46.694
Target's holding.

06:46.762 --> 06:48.629
Is that--

06:48.697 --> 06:50.764
is that right?

06:55.136 --> 06:57.603
Okay, we've got
a second target.

06:57.671 --> 06:59.805
What do you mean
a second target?

06:59.873 --> 07:01.239
Is this right?

07:01.307 --> 07:02.274
I think so.

07:02.341 --> 07:04.175
Okay, now we have
three targets.

07:04.243 --> 07:05.877
What the hell
is happening?

07:05.944 --> 07:07.611
I don't know, sir.

07:11.683 --> 07:13.617
Okay, now we have
five targets.

07:13.684 --> 07:16.519
They keep coming.

07:16.587 --> 07:18.321
Have Simon move
his men in.

07:18.389 --> 07:19.389
Yes, sir.

